name: THS
description: Themis Protocol is the largest and most active protocol on Filecoin-FEVM as well as the highest TVL, and is the cornerstone protocol of the Filecoin eco-financial layer.THS is the platform token for Themis Pro and Themis Swap. 70% of Themis Pro's trading fees and position profits are used to repurchase THS, and 33% of Themis Swap's trading fees are used to repurchase THS in a highly deflationary model.
